<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:08:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与真主党的战争是不可避免的。但以色列应该发起这一行动吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</link><description>以色列现在应对真主党及其挑衅有重要的战略理由。但黎巴嫩战争可能会将美国自由派选民中不断高涨的反以色列情绪转变为一场完美风暴。这将是一场以色列从未经历过的冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子被控刺伤妻子、打伤儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</link><description>起诉书指控 Asher Bohbot 对其 15 岁的儿子犯有严重谋杀罪和严重殴打罪，当时儿子在事件中试图阻止他。一位家人的熟人表示，布布特以前殴打过他的妻子，她曾考虑与他离婚</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</guid></item><item><title>从被毁坏的家中撤离后，来自加沙边境的以色列孩子在特拉维夫重新开始学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</link><description>大约三周前，大约 400 名雷伊姆居民从最南端城市埃拉特的酒店房间收拾行李，他们在 10 月 7 日袭击事件后从家中撤离后一直住在那里，开始了生活的新篇章。这次是在特拉维夫的赫茨尔街</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡违反利益冲突协议的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</link><description>“据我们所知，自10月7日以来，以色列一直处于战争状态，这对我们面前的案件产生了重大影响。在这些影响中，作为请愿者主张核心的立法程序目前并未得到推进，”高等法院法官说</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院加沙种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</link><description>以色列外交部发言人称南非律师为“哈马斯”代表，周五第二天听证会前已做出初步回应</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</guid></item><item><title>汗尤尼斯的“720度”战斗，可能决定以色列与哈马斯战争的结果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</link><description>双桅船。驻扎在加沙地带南部的以色列陆军第 98 师指挥官丹·戈德福斯 (Dan Goldfus) 将军每天都在解决像魔方一样的问题，因为他监督着一支在地面、空中和哈马斯隧道中行动的臃肿部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列政府意图消灭加沙的巴勒斯坦人”：南非向国际法院提出种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</link><description>南非法律团队在海牙进行了开庭陈词，指责以色列的种族灭绝行为、言论和煽动行为。他们引用了内塔尼亚胡总理、赫尔佐格总统和几位部长的声明作为证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔否认哈马斯领导人流亡条款，以色列回应新的人质释放提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</link><description>政治消息人士强调，以色列的一贯立场不是同意哈马斯停止战争的要求，也不是以完全停止在加沙地带的军事活动为前提达成释放人质协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:21:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</guid></item><item><title>1986年以来失踪士兵的女儿罗恩·阿拉德：以色列政界人士必须就释放人质进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</link><description>尤瓦尔·阿拉德在脸书上写道，“因为历史不仅在我眼前重演，而且人们似乎拒绝从历史中吸取教训”，并警告应立即将人质带回家</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技行业的情况会变得更糟吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</link><description>去年是初创国家有史以来最糟糕的一年。现在，2024 年将会出现更多战争、腐败政府和持续的全球经济衰退</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人因玩枪误杀朋友而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</link><description>自以色列国家安全部降低申请和领取持枪许可证的条件以来，已发生多起涉枪伤亡事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 10:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</guid></item><item><title>枪械如何成为以色列必备的时尚潮流</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，枪支已经从一种防护手段转变为一种身份象征和宣言</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 09:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</link><description>海牙国际法院听取了南非的指控，指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝，但未能惩罚煽动种族灭绝的人。检方援引总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格和以色列部长的声明作为种族灭绝意图的证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 06:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的共和党对手在爱荷华州辩论中就以色列和反犹太主义问题发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</link><description>美国前驻联合国特使尼基·黑利（Nikki Haley）猛烈抨击佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯（Ron DeSantis）未能充分打击家乡的新纳粹游行和反犹太主义，而德桑蒂斯则指责总统。拜登称美军在中东“任人宰割”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员告诉国土报，世界法院不太可能在加沙种族灭绝听证会上下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</link><description>预计以色列将于周五在海牙国际法院对指控提出反驳</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望建立一个“新的巴勒斯坦权力机构”来统治加沙。作为交换，阿巴斯希望建国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯支持巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯建立巴勒斯坦国的步骤，但华盛顿说服以色列做出让步并不容易，这个问题可能会使其与内塔尼亚胡政府发生冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</guid></item><item><title>从黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹击中以色列北部城镇的几所房屋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</link><description>以色列高等法院驳回因战争而罢黜内塔尼亚胡的请愿 ■ 以色列挫败了两名东耶路撒冷居民策划的伊斯兰国袭击 ■ 国际法院在海牙举行的种族灭绝听证会今天结束；以色列周五就指控进行辩护 ■ 以色列国防军发现法医证据，证明哈马斯在汗尤尼斯地下新发现的隧道中扣押了人质 ■ 布林肯表示，以色列与该地区合作，开辟通往巴勒斯坦国的道路，将孤立伊朗</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:21:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以潜在暴力为由取消了特拉维夫犹太-阿拉伯和平抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</link><description>计划在“只有和平才能带来安全”的旗帜下集会的组织者发誓要向最高法院的裁决提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列未成年人因间谍罪入狱 18 个月。调查显示他是以色列国防军情报人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</link><description>这名当时 17 岁的年轻人被指控发布高度敏感信息，但警方未能按照军方官员的要求彻底调查他的说法。此后经军事情报部门核实，但未告知检方</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会批准决议要求也门胡塞武装立即停止袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</link><description>安理会还呼吁胡塞武装释放银河领袖号，这是一艘由日本运营的车辆运输公司，与该组织上个月征用的一名以色列商人有联系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 23:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>